{"tid":2250330,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國首相約翰遜擬明年初辭職，據說因為人工太低不足以生活","createTime":"2020-10-20T04:45:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-20T05:28:09.000Z","uid":118346,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"28a288476e1bacaecb5160445145e90edffb04fd","tid":2250330,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T04:45:48.000Z","msg":"據英國《大都市報》消息，英國首相約翰遜計劃在明年春季辭職。消息人士指，約翰遜稱自己出任首相年薪僅15萬英鎊（約150萬港元），人工比他出任前還要低，認為該年薪不足以生活。<br />\n<br />\n報導引述消息人士，約翰遜向其黨友投訴指，其年薪只有15萬英鎊，但他不僅要撫養6個孩子，還要向前妻支付一大筆離婚的費用，該年薪令他難以負擔。報導還指，約翰遜希望能在半年內解決脫歐，並帶英國走出疫情，然後辭職。<br />\n<br />\n在約翰遜出任首相前，他在《電訊報》撰寫專欄，每月可賺2.3萬英鎊（約23萬港元），而他不時應邀發表演說就可以賺到數十萬英鎊。<br />\n<br />\n約翰遜在2019年7月23日的英國保守黨黨魁投票中大勝，並於翌日（24日）正式接任英國首相。"},{"pid":"f92d303530a2769e61f64468ed5db1b8aa7d3b10","tid":2250330,"uid":155095,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T04:47:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://obs.line-scdn.net/0hVbb7RBNMCU1fTiGh0b52GmUYCiJsIhpOO3hYUgAgV3kmdx0SYXhAI3xPVX93e04TMXpPKHhJEnwhLEhLMyBA/w580\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fobs.line-scdn.net%2F0hVbb7RBNMCU1fTiGh0b52GmUYCiJsIhpOO3hYUgAgV3kmdx0SYXhAI3xPVX93e04TMXpPKHhJEnwhLEhLMyBA%2Fw580&h=1b829920&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9f4fad2969147dde70b3c6a0ce4f7168efbdfc85","tid":2250330,"uid":131323,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T04:48:05.000Z","msg":"人工太低 不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca05940c7391d26159c42ea134ab456db74dda68","tid":2250330,"uid":81273,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T04:50:51.000Z","msg":"林鄭屌打你"},{"pid":"a20c3dd2b6fb8399371d1c8cd491a59cc5556e3f","tid":2250330,"uid":89861,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T04:53:42.000Z","msg":"扣埋稅仲低人工過黑警督察"},{"pid":"000441f055c9bbaea7cf3d5566f6120d3cbe522a","tid":2250330,"uid":149494,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T04:54:04.000Z","msg":"條友之前搞咁多野都係想做首相<br />\n而家又嫌錢少<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95e7dbdd3ffd9f5e5879845b5c408d149757558d","tid":2250330,"uid":100016,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T05:28:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}